import React, {useState} from 'react';
import { Typography } from '@material-ui/core';
import { Button } from '@material-ui/core';
import {Grid} from '@material-ui/core';
import MailOutlineIcon from '@material-ui/icons/MailOutline';


const HomePage = () => {

    const [toggle, setToggle] = useState(false);

    return (<>
        {/* <div style={{backgroundImage:`url(${"images/mcewanhall.jpg"})`,
        backgroundPosition: 'center',
        backgroundSize: 'cover',
        backgroundRepeat: 'no-repeat',
        height:'750px',
        opacity:'75%'}}> */}
            <Grid container
            direction="row"
            justify="flex-start"
            alignItems="left"
            style={{background: 'rgba(205, 255, 219, 0.7)'}}>

                <Grid item sm={6} xs={0}>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item sm={6} xs={12}>
                    <Typography
                    display="block"
                    justifyContent="center"
                    align="left"
                    variant="h4"
                    style={{opacity:'100%', color:'black', paddingRight:'30px', paddingTop:'20px', paddingLeft:'0', paddingBottom:'0px', fontWeight:'bold'}}>
                        Hey, I'm
                    </Typography>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item sm={6} xs={0}>
                </Grid>

                <Grid item sm={6} xs={6}>
                    <Typography
                    display="block"
                    justifyContent="center"
                    align="left"
                    variant="h2"
                    style={{opacity:'100%', color:'black', paddingRight:'30px', paddingTop:'0', paddingLeft:'0', paddingBottom:'20px', fontWeight:'bold'}}>
                    Andrea Husseiniova
                    </Typography>   
                </Grid>

                <Grid item sm={6} xs={0}></Grid>

                <Grid item sm={6} xs={12}>
                    <Button 
                    onClick = {()=>(
                        setToggle(!toggle)
                    )}
                    variant="outlined" style={{color:'black', border:'1px solid black'}}>
                        Get to know me
                    </Button>
                    <Typography variant='h2' color='black' className={`paragraph ${toggle&&'active'}`}> Hiiiiiiii</Typography>
                </Grid>
                
            </Grid>
    </>
    )
}

export default HomePage;
